fix(adopt): also gate Forget out of the standalone Detail drawer

The chooser context-menu gate added in the previous commit was a
partial fix — adopted installs (sourceId: 'standalone') also rendered
untrackAction() in the Manage drawer's pinBottom "Actions" group via
src/main/sources/standalone/updateSections.ts, so the user could still
Forget them from there.

Conditionally drop untrackAction() when installation.adopted, matching
the chooser gate. Delete stays available either way.
